  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/eec29fa99b793b2cae8f40f38af57e61.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=132 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Minutes in Hell</strong> is a 4-player online co-op extraction horror game with roguelite progression. You and your team of contestants are dropped into randomized, trap-filled arenas with one goal: survive the game show. Scavenge for loot, dodge deadly traps, and outrun the terrifying \"Employees\" to secure your winnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Proximity Voice Chat:</strong> Communication is survival. Use fully integrated proximity voice chat to coordinate with your team, call out trap locations, and scream for help. But be careful—panic is contagious, and the \"Employees\" are listening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Progression:</strong> Your Greenroom is your lifeline. Invest your winnings into permanent upgrades that persist between runs. Buy the <strong>Slushie Machine</strong> to gain perks against the Gelly Cube, or upgrade your furniture to boost your stats. Even if you die in the arena, your Greenroom investments remain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/ce07fd3a6261be4033fac7f2e3030f87.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/ce07fd3a6261be4033fac7f2e3030f87.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/ce07fd3a6261be4033fac7f2e3030f87.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The \"Employees\":</strong> You aren't alone in the arena. Survive against a roster of unique monsters including <strong>Buckethead</strong>, the <strong>Jiangshi</strong>, <strong>Giant Rats</strong>, and the terrifying <strong>Mannequin</strong>. Each enemy has unique behaviors you must learn to survive—or you'll end up dead on camera.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/151fd84031464de5a863533756e2a5dc.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/151fd84031464de5a863533756e2a5dc.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/151fd84031464de5a863533756e2a5dc.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sponsors & Gear:</strong> Visit the shop to buy equipment that can turn the tide. Upgrade your storage with <strong>Backpacks</strong>, power electronics with <strong>Batteries</strong>, set traps with <strong>Rakes</strong>, or buy the ultimate last resort: a <strong>Gun with One Bullet</strong>. Make your shot count.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonus Rounds:</strong> What would a gameshow be without Bonus Rounds?! Complete specific challenges during your run to win extra cash and maximize your payout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Stakes Extraction:</strong> You have limited time to navigate the maze, grab the cash, and find the exit. If you die in the arena, you lose your current loot haul. Will you play it safe to bank your cash, or risk it all for the grand prize?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Minutes in Hell</strong> is a 4-player online co-op extraction horror game with roguelite progression. You and your team of contestants are dropped into randomized, trap-filled arenas with one goal: survive the game show. Scavenge for loot, dodge deadly traps, and outrun the terrifying \"Employees\" to secure your winnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/2cf874a46dde69e4ff0b2209f7794d0f.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Proximity Voice Chat:</strong> Communication is survival. Use fully integrated proximity voice chat to coordinate with your team, call out trap locations, and scream for help. But be careful—panic is contagious, and the \"Employees\" are listening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Progression:</strong> Your Greenroom is your lifeline. Invest your winnings into permanent upgrades that persist between runs. Buy the <strong>Slushie Machine</strong> to gain perks against the Gelly Cube, or upgrade your furniture to boost your stats. Even if you die in the arena, your Greenroom investments remain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/