 ><strong>Bonus Rounds:</strong> What would a gameshow be without Bonus Rounds?! Complete specific challenges during your run to win extra cash and maximize your payout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.poster.avif?t=1765510669\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.webm?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750480/extras/87d32b6bc1e4071b1c044a051271a50e.mp4?t=1765510669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Stakes Extraction:</strong> You have limited time to navigate the maze, grab the cash, and find the exit. If you die in the arena, you lose your current loot haul. Will you play it safe to bank your cash, or risk it all for the grand prize?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
